title: Draft Needs for Top 10 Midseason & Will Grier Interview
itunes:title: Draft Needs for Top 10 Midseason & Will Grier Interview
description:
In a jam packed episode, DJ and Bucky examine the Bills MNF loss to NE (:30), draft needs for top 10 midseason, including New York’s next QB and potential offensive weapons for the Cardinals (2:45), then West Virginia University QB Will Grier joins the show to discuss his biggest hero and highlight of his college career (8:30) & lastly, the guys share some takeaways from the week that was in CFB (26:25).
